SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.BRANCH,B.MIS_GROUP, B.MIS_GROUP_TXN, B.MIS_GROUP_COMP, B.POOL_CODE, B.TXN_MIS_1, B.TXN_MIS_2, B.TXN_MIS_3, B.TXN_MIS_4, B.TXN_MIS_5, B.TXN_MIS_6, B.TXN_MIS_7, B.TXN_MIS_8, B.TXN_MIS_9, B.TXN_MIS_10, B.COMP_MIS_1, B.COMP_MIS_2, B.COMP_MIS_3, B.COMP_MIS_4, B.COMP_MIS_5, B.COMP_MIS_6, B.COMP_MIS_7, B.COMP_MIS_8, B.COMP_MIS_9, B.COMP_MIS_10, B.COST_CODE1, B.COST_CODE2, B.COST_CODE3, B.COST_CODE4, B.COST_CODE5 FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CLASS_MAPPING B WHERE A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.UNIT_REF_NO AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A'

SELECT A.AC_GL_NO, B.MIS_GROUP, B.MIS_GROUP_TXN, B.MIS_GROUP_COMP, B.POOL_CODE, B.TXN_MIS_1, B.TXN_MIS_2, B.TXN_MIS_3, B.TXN_MIS_4, B.TXN_MIS_5, B.TXN_MIS_6, B.TXN_MIS_7, B.TXN_MIS_8, B.TXN_MIS_9, B.TXN_MIS_10, B.COMP_MIS_1, B.COMP_MIS_2, B.COMP_MIS_3, B.COMP_MIS_4, B.COMP_MIS_5, B.COMP_MIS_6, B.COMP_MIS_7, B.COMP_MIS_8, B.COMP_MIS_9, B.COMP_MIS_10, B.COST_CODE1, B.COST_CODE2, B.COST_CODE3, B.COST_CODE4, B.COST_CODE5 FROM OLTB_ACCOUNT A, OLTBS_CLASS_MAPPING B WHERE A.AC_GL_NO = B.UNIT_REF_NO AND A.BRANCH_CODE = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH AND A.AUTH_STAT = 'A' AND A.AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM OLVWS_PROD_ACNT_ACCESS X WHERE X.AC_GL_NO = A.AC_GL_NO AND X.PRODUCT_CODE = ?)
